af around each salmon sandwich to securely enclose."},{"content":"Place parcels in Varoma dish, cover and place Varoma into position. Steam <b>18 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Serve hot garnished with lime wedges."}],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","45m","4 portions"]}